---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Guerreiro.IA | Victor Guerreiro" description="Victor Guerreiro construye sistemas inteligentes, recomendacion y consultoria tecnica en IA para problemas reales." locale="en">
  <section class="grid items-start gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.12fr_0.88fr] lg:gap-14">
    <div class="animate-fadeIn">
      <div class="pill animate-shimmer inline-flex rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-accent">
        IA aplicada para producto, decisiones y operacion
      </div>

      <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-semibold leading-[0.95] text-slate-50 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        Inteligencia artificial con
        <span class="display-title italic text-accent"> profundidad tecnica </span>
        y entrega practica.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-muted sm:text-xl">
        Desarrollo sistemas de recomendacion, ranking y arquitectura de IA para contextos donde la calidad de decision necesita impacto medible.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/en/engagements" class="cta-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
          Ver formatos de trabajo
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
          Escribirme
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-g-b2014a11b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em]">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="surface rounded-[1.5rem] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Foco</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-200">Recomendacion, optimizacion e inferencia aplicada.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface rounded-[1.5rem] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Formato</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-200">Investigacion aplicada y consultoria tecnica orientada a valor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="surface rounded-[1.5rem] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Contexto</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-200">Productos digitales, gobierno y decisiones de alto impacto.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="animate-fadeIn surface relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(139,246,209,0.24),transparent_70%)]"></div>
      <img src="/perfil.jpg" alt="Victor Guerreiro portrait" class="relative z-10 mx-auto h-36 w-36 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 object-cover shadow-[0_18px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)] sm:h-44 sm:w-44" />

      <div class="relative z-10 mt-8 space-y-5 text-left">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-400">Victor Guerreiro</p>
          <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-50">Consultoria tecnica con base en investigacion.</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-300">
            Si tienes un problema ambiguo y de alto costo de error, te ayudo a definir arquitectura, experimentos y direccion de producto con criterio tecnico.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>
</Layout>
